OL,4,Chomelessness, Shelter charity finds
OL,6,FOne in 28 children in Hastings are
OL,7,Fhomeless and living in temporary
OL,8,Faccommodation, according to new
OL,9,Ffigures by the homelessness charity
OL,10,FShelter.
OL,12,FIt says many young people are living
OL,13,Fin cramped, unsafe and unhealthy
OL,14,Fconditions for prolonged periods.
OL,16,FIssues facing families include
OL,17,Fdangerous mould, faulty wiring and
OL,18,Finfestations.
